'''connector'''

#A device (or, more precisely, a [[mating]] pair of devices, often a [[plug]] and a [[socket]]) for connecting together two [[wire]]s, [[cable]]s, or [[hose]]s, allowing electricity or fluid to flow but also allowing easy disconnection and reconnection when necessary.

